data.description: Gorgeous move-in ready home w/tons of upgrades in Elkins Lake! Whole home generator. Enjoy being close to nature with the beautiful, enclosed back patio w/ surround sound. Enjoy lovely arches leading from the formal dining room into the spacious & open living room. Soaring ceilings, built-ins, a large fireplace, & beautiful wood-look porcelain tile floors make the living room a perfect place to gather. The kitchen features granite counters, large island w/seating, stainless steel appliances, unique backsplash, & lots of cabinet space. Retreat to the primary bedroom w/an en-suite featuring a spa-like bath w/custom tiled walk-in shower, dual vanities, pedestal tub, & TWO large walk-in closets, one with easy access to the laundry! Two more bedrooms downstairs & a full bath w/dual sinks. Half story upstairs. Tankless water heater! Uninstalled flooring provided in shed for primary, upstairs, & downstairs bedrooms. Fall in love w/ all the community amenities & lakes in the development!
